i3 is installed with speach enabled by default.
In addition we enable autologin to prevent screen reader accesibility issues.
The following are the packages we are installing:

i3
lightdm
lightdm-gtk-greeter
lightdm-gtk-greeter-settings
accountsservice
espeakup
brltty
pulseaudio
pulseaudio-alsa
alsa-utils
speech-dispatcher
libwnck3
lsof
espeak-ng
orca
sound-theme-freedesktop
mate-terminal
